(339, '<p align="center">\r\n	&nbsp;<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">来源：中国投影网</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ''Arial'', ''sans-serif''; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ''Arial'', ''sans-serif''; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">在正在举行的第二十二届北京国际广播电影电视设备展览会</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ''Arial'', ''sans-serif''; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">(BIRTV2013)</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">上，作为国内领先的信号切换和传输产品供应商，</span><span style="font-family: ''Arial'', ''sans-serif''; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"> </span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">大连科迪展示了全系列的数字高清产品。</span></font></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-f