language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">&rdquo;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">在高清领域有着五年多来的深入探索，并一直保持着技术优势，走在国内同行业的最前沿，在本次展会上，科迪分四大展区全面展示了科迪在信号传输及切换播出方面的领先产品，包括支持</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ''Arial'', ''sans-serif''; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">3G</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">并自适应模拟、标清、高清的高端产品，代表着当代信息技术应用的最高水平。</span></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><img alt="" src="../upload/img/2013082302.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 200px" /></span></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-