i-font-family: Arial">和</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: ''Arial'', ''sans-serif''; font-size: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">3G-SDI</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">信号的检测能力更是目前国内仅有。无论是从模块化插板式设计还是从超大规模等方面都体现了大连科迪在国内的技术领先优势，其性能指标及稳定性均满足或优于国家甲级标准。</span></span></span></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><img alt="" src="../upload/img/2013082303.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 200px" /></span></span></span></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-languag