到静音要求，自适应线缆均衡功能，能自动对输入串行数字信号进行线缆均衡，延长信号源到播出切换器的传输距离，有效地解决了数字信号的传输问题，更具备掉电直通功能以及掉电记忆功能等特点，保证系统的播出安全。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><img alt="" src="../upload/img/2013082304.jpg" style="width: 300px; height: 200px" /></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-languag