</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 100px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					反射损耗</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 232px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					&gt;18dB@5MHz～540MHz</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 70px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					控制协议</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 237px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					9600波特率,8位,1位停止位,无校验位</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 100px; height: 17px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					信号幅度</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 232px; height: 17px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					800mV&plusmn;5%</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 70px; height: 17px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					连接器</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 237px; height: 17px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					9针 D 型口、2-RX、3-TX、5-GND</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 100px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					阻抗</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 232px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					75&Omega;</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 70px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					选配接口</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 237px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					TCP/IP、RS-422、RS-485</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 100px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					均衡</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 232px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					0～300m Belden 1694A</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 70px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					控制软件</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 237px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					Kedi 用于 XP/Vista/Win 7</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="width: 332px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="left">\r\n					视频输出</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td colspan="2" style="width: 307px; height: 18px">\r\n				<p align="