(204, NULL, ',193', '<p>\r\n	<strong>功能特点</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;300MHz~400MHz高视频带宽；</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 支持场逆程切换，保持切换瞬间画面完整，切换速度更快；</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 多层电路板保证信号极强的抗干扰性能；</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 缓冲的输入和输出提供没有串扰的高质量视频及音频信号；</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 具有可标签输入输出端按键；</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 具有掉电记忆功能；</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 具有多个RS-232、RS-422、RS-485通讯接口；</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 具有TCP/IP（以太网）控制接口；</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 90～260V/AC&nbsp; 50/60Hz 电源，适于全球范围使用。</p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<strong>简介</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 科迪VGA 矩阵是专门用来传输高解析度计算机信号的矩阵，用于将各路VGA 计算机输入信号切换到任意输出通道，分辨率支持 VGA~UXGA，同时支持 1080p 以上分辨率，支持 RS-232、RS-422、RS-485、TCP/IP 控制，适用于任何规模的 VGA信号的传输应用，已广泛应用于安防监控领域。</p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<strong>技术指标</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 120px; height: 6px">\r\n				<p>\r\n					信号格式</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 432px; height: 6px">\r\n				<p>\r\n					VGA信号</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 120px; height: 6px">\r\n				<p>\r\n					接口形式</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 432px; height: 6px">\r\n				<p>\r\n					15针D-Sub</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 120px; height: 6px">\r\n				<p>\r\n					带宽</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 432px; height: 6px">\r\n				<p>\r\n					&ge;300MHz</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style="width: 120px; height: 6px">\r\n				<p>\r\n					分辨率</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td style="width: 432px; height: 6px">\r\n				<p>\r\n					最高支持1920&times;1200@60Hz</p>\r\n			</td>